WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:00:18.940 --> 00:00:23.880
♪Only after bloom comes fruit♪

00:00:25.290 --> 00:00:29.260
♪Who says glory must fade to the past♪

00:00:31.920 --> 00:00:37.010
♪Only through thunder
do you reach the clouds♪

00:00:38.210 --> 00:00:43.120
♪Who made you the crown of every peak♪

00:00:44.650 --> 00:00:47.930
♪I stand at the center of the stage♪

00:00:47.930 --> 00:00:51.000
♪My shadow is pinned against the wall♪

00:00:51.710 --> 00:00:56.660
♪Facing the light earns every medal♪

00:00:57.700 --> 00:01:00.880
♪Little birds,
save your needless pecking♪

00:01:00.880 --> 00:01:04.160
♪The open sky rises high♪

00:01:04.700 --> 00:01:09.830
♪When night falls,
the moon begins to shine♪

00:01:10.600 --> 00:01:13.860
♪I stand in the heart of these lands♪

00:01:13.860 --> 00:01:17.220
♪My shadow bears no crown or robe♪

00:01:17.630 --> 00:01:23.300
♪Then I know truth needs no disguise♪

00:01:23.710 --> 00:01:26.960
♪The green hills see me as I am♪

00:01:26.960 --> 00:01:30.290
♪Like dew, lightning,
and moon on the river♪

00:01:30.690 --> 00:01:34.730
♪Showing me exactly who I am♪

00:01:34.730 --> 00:01:35.980
=The Lead=

00:01:36.060 --> 00:01:37.940
=Episode 8=

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:44.110
This is Mr. Qin.

00:01:45.190 --> 00:01:46.280
- Shoes Bai.
- Hello.

00:01:46.400 --> 00:01:47.560
Mr. Qin's spouse.

00:01:47.800 --> 00:01:48.640
Hello.

00:01:49.350 --> 00:01:50.190
Where is he?

00:02:18.200 --> 00:02:19.040
Sir.

00:02:19.790 --> 00:02:21.840
We got drenched in sweat today.

00:02:22.320 --> 00:02:24.470
Can we bathe by the river later?

00:02:24.470 --> 00:02:26.280
Yeah, we're all sticky.

00:02:27.200 --> 00:02:28.040
Comrades,

00:02:28.430 --> 00:02:29.560
don't worry.

00:02:30.070 --> 00:02:32.350
We've arranged all of that for you.

00:02:32.350 --> 00:02:33.640
The female troupe members

00:02:33.640 --> 00:02:36.390
can just bathe without any worries.

00:02:37.460 --> 00:02:38.320
That's great!

00:02:38.320 --> 00:02:41.430
♪Who helped us stand tall again♪

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:01.310
You'll

00:03:01.310 --> 00:03:03.590
spend a long time together.

00:03:03.590 --> 00:03:05.560
You'll be fellow disciples for life.

00:03:06.150 --> 00:03:08.070
Get along with them.

00:03:08.070 --> 00:03:10.000
Don't let yourself get left out, okay?

00:03:10.790 --> 00:03:11.710
Caixiang.

00:03:13.560 --> 00:03:14.480
Thank you

00:03:15.120 --> 00:03:16.710
for letting me play Li Tiemei.

00:03:18.640 --> 00:03:19.640
It wasn't up to me.

00:03:20.310 --> 00:03:21.230
The role chose you.

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:24.680
Sanyuan really gets you.

00:03:26.430 --> 00:03:27.280
What do you mean?

00:03:27.280 --> 00:03:29.400
He said what you love is the stage,

00:03:29.840 --> 00:03:31.950
while I love the fame it brings me.

00:03:34.400 --> 00:03:35.430
I love both.

00:03:37.200 --> 00:03:38.040
I didn't ask you.

00:03:39.760 --> 00:03:40.790
Know what that's called?

00:03:43.230 --> 00:03:44.590
Having it both ways.

00:03:49.630 --> 00:03:50.800
Where did your uncle go tonight?

00:03:51.120 --> 00:03:52.680
He wasn't there for noodles.

00:03:57.560 --> 00:03:58.870
Eat and chat.

00:03:59.800 --> 00:04:00.960
Call me if you need me.

00:04:01.280 --> 00:04:02.120
Go ahead.

00:04:02.430 --> 00:04:03.840
Sanyuan and I are

00:04:03.840 --> 00:04:05.080
discussing heroes over food and drinks.

00:04:06.240 --> 00:04:07.280
Sanyuan.

00:04:08.750 --> 00:04:09.630
Mr. Qin,

00:04:09.960 --> 00:04:10.800
a toast to you.

00:04:14.240 --> 00:04:15.080
How is it?

00:04:16.150 --> 00:04:16.990
Great.

00:04:17.470 --> 00:04:18.710
It went right to my head.

00:04:19.470 --> 00:04:20.560
Have some food.

00:04:23.910 --> 00:04:26.190
Freshly ground tofu tastes so good.

00:04:31.280 --> 00:04:33.150
That man of Shoes Bai's,

00:04:33.470 --> 00:04:34.470
how did he end up here?

00:04:36.280 --> 00:04:39.800
He studied in the Soviet Union.

00:04:39.800 --> 00:04:42.280
He was an accomplished orchestra conductor.

00:04:44.470 --> 00:04:46.560
We met back in the provincial capital.

00:04:47.150 --> 00:04:48.430
Now, he's

00:04:50.030 --> 00:04:50.870
in

00:04:51.030 --> 00:04:52.630
a place over ten miles from here,

00:04:53.280 --> 00:04:54.150
deep in the mountains.

00:04:56.120 --> 00:04:57.430
It's been three years.

00:04:58.030 --> 00:05:00.120
They never got to be together.

00:05:01.150 --> 00:05:02.400
Then he heard your troupe

00:05:02.630 --> 00:05:03.800
was performing here.

00:05:04.430 --> 00:05:06.000
So he snuck out

00:05:06.680 --> 00:05:07.750
to see her.

00:05:09.400 --> 00:05:11.280
He has to be back before dawn.

00:05:11.910 --> 00:05:13.150
He can't let anyone find out.

00:05:17.030 --> 00:05:19.750
That's over ten miles of mountain road.

00:05:21.080 --> 00:05:25.240
♪Grandma♪

00:05:25.840 --> 00:05:29.240
♪Tells of♪

00:05:30.080 --> 00:05:39.630
♪The brave old days♪

00:05:45.560 --> 00:05:47.000
Chu Jiahe, why'd you stop singing?

00:05:47.000 --> 00:05:48.280
Yeah, why'd you stop?

00:05:48.590 --> 00:05:49.590
Yeah, why?

00:05:49.590 --> 00:05:50.520
Whose feet?

00:05:50.870 --> 00:05:52.390
- So stinky.
- Not mine.

00:05:52.390 --> 00:05:55.270
- Not mine, either.
- Not mine.

00:05:55.270 --> 00:05:56.110
Yu Liping.

00:05:56.270 --> 00:05:58.040
Yu Liping, is it yours?

00:05:58.040 --> 00:05:59.430
No. I checked.

00:06:00.120 --> 00:06:01.040
Stop it.

00:06:01.040 --> 00:06:03.190
Yi Qing'e, it's yours.

00:06:03.190 --> 00:06:04.030
No.

00:06:05.190 --> 00:06:06.510
It is. Your shoes stink.

00:06:06.800 --> 00:06:07.870
It's not me.

00:06:07.870 --> 00:06:08.800
How is it not?

00:06:08.800 --> 00:06:10.560
The smell's coming from your side.

00:06:10.560 --> 00:06:11.630
Smell it, everyone.

00:06:11.630 --> 00:06:13.510
She's right.

00:06:13.510 --> 00:06:15.040
- So stinky.
- Just get out.

00:06:15.040 --> 00:06:15.910
So stinky!

00:06:15.910 --> 00:06:18.360
Yi Qing'e, take your shoes and get out.

00:06:18.360 --> 00:06:19.200
Get out.

00:06:19.210 --> 00:06:22.000
Get out. Get out. Get out.

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:24.630
Get out. Get out. Get out.

00:06:24.630 --> 00:06:27.000
Get out. Get out. Get out.

00:06:27.000 --> 00:06:28.560
- Shut the door.
- Get out.

00:06:28.830 --> 00:06:29.830
So annoying.

00:06:33.120 --> 00:06:34.680
Jiahe, keep singing.

00:06:39.120 --> 00:06:40.070
Go easy.

00:06:43.070 --> 00:06:44.270
You're pushing me too far.

00:06:57.950 --> 00:06:58.920
Go easy.

00:06:58.920 --> 00:07:02.060
(Together)

00:07:02.390 --> 00:07:03.230
What?

00:07:06.800 --> 00:07:07.640
Someone's here.

00:07:07.870 --> 00:07:09.430
What? You scared me.

00:07:09.880 --> 00:07:10.750
What are you doing here?

00:07:10.750 --> 00:07:11.680
Stargazing.

00:07:12.560 --> 00:07:14.190
Go on. I need to pee.

00:07:14.190 --> 00:07:15.030
Don't look.

00:07:33.630 --> 00:07:35.310
What do you want to eat tomorrow?

00:07:36.390 --> 00:07:38.560
Ask Master Song to make us some

00:07:38.560 --> 00:07:40.120
cold Jiangshui noodles, maybe?

00:07:40.430 --> 00:07:41.270
Sure.

00:07:41.640 --> 00:07:42.480
No problem.

00:07:42.600 --> 00:07:43.750
I'll tell him tomorrow.

00:07:43.750 --> 00:07:44.680
Okay, thanks.

00:07:50.190 --> 00:07:51.030
Where's Shoes Bai?

00:07:51.480 --> 00:07:52.830
Have you seen Shoes Bai?

00:07:52.830 --> 00:07:54.270
She doesn't like the shared dorm.

00:07:54.270 --> 00:07:56.600
Maybe she went to the costume shed.

00:07:56.600 --> 00:07:57.510
No way.

00:07:57.920 --> 00:07:59.000
Her bedding roll is

00:07:59.000 --> 00:07:59.920
still here.

00:08:00.630 --> 00:08:02.040
Where could she go this late?

00:08:02.830 --> 00:08:04.270
When we were bathing earlier,

00:08:04.560 --> 00:08:05.560
did any of you see her?

00:08:05.560 --> 00:08:06.870
- I didn't notice.
- Didn't see her.

00:08:06.870 --> 00:08:07.950
I didn't notice, either.

00:08:08.680 --> 00:08:09.520
There's a deep pool.

00:08:09.530 --> 00:08:10.560
She didn't fall in, did she?

00:08:11.310 --> 00:08:12.750
Stop talking nonsense.

00:08:12.750 --> 00:08:14.630
Maybe she's in the costume shed.

00:08:14.630 --> 00:08:16.270
- Right.
- I'll check the costume shed.

00:08:16.270 --> 00:08:17.110
You, come with me.

00:08:17.290 --> 00:08:18.130
Okay.

00:08:18.140 --> 00:08:19.190
- You come, too.
- Okay.

00:08:19.190 --> 00:08:20.120
Bring a flashlight.

00:08:27.750 --> 00:08:29.120
We...

00:08:29.920 --> 00:08:31.190
Enough. Stop shouting.

00:08:32.310 --> 00:08:33.270
Where's Hu Sanyuan?

00:08:34.040 --> 00:08:36.000
You're asking me? I was asking you.

00:08:36.390 --> 00:08:38.000
He vanished right after the show.

00:08:39.390 --> 00:08:40.430
Where could he have gone?

00:08:40.750 --> 00:08:42.000
This is his hometown.

00:08:42.270 --> 00:08:43.950
He must've slipped off to an old flame.

00:08:45.310 --> 00:08:46.390
Knock it off.

00:08:46.830 --> 00:08:48.120
- He Dachui.
- What?

00:08:48.120 --> 00:08:49.390
Have you seen Shoes Bai?

00:08:49.630 --> 00:08:50.830
- Shoes Bai?
- No.

00:08:50.950 --> 00:08:52.000
We went to bathe.

00:08:52.270 --> 00:08:53.190
How would we have seen her?

00:08:53.190 --> 00:08:54.120
Exactly.

00:08:54.720 --> 00:08:56.000
I'd actually like to see her.

00:08:57.190 --> 00:08:58.360
She is missing.

00:08:59.430 --> 00:09:00.430
Not in the costume shed either?

00:09:00.550 --> 00:09:01.390
No.

00:09:01.390 --> 00:09:02.870
Where could she go in such a strange place?

00:09:03.270 --> 00:09:04.270
Gather some people

00:09:04.270 --> 00:09:05.270
and search along the river.

00:09:05.830 --> 00:09:06.920
We'll report to Director Huang.

00:09:06.920 --> 00:09:08.630
Okay, I'll gather the kids as well.

00:09:08.630 --> 00:09:09.470
Go, go.

00:09:09.920 --> 00:09:10.950
- We'll go first.
- Let's go.

00:09:10.950 --> 00:09:11.790
Which way?

00:09:12.010 --> 00:09:12.920
Just follow the ditch.

00:09:12.920 --> 00:09:13.760
Hurry.

00:09:14.040 --> 00:09:15.160
Move it.

00:09:24.270 --> 00:09:25.600
How far is your hometown?

00:09:26.630 --> 00:09:28.070
Half a day on foot.

00:09:28.870 --> 00:09:29.750
Can buses get there?

00:09:30.510 --> 00:09:32.070
Only bikes can.

00:09:33.680 --> 00:09:34.520
Fall in.

00:09:34.830 --> 00:09:35.670
Quit messing around.

00:09:35.800 --> 00:09:36.640
Fall in.

00:09:37.270 --> 00:09:38.430
Fall in, fall in!

00:09:39.480 --> 00:09:40.750
What are you two doing here?

00:09:40.750 --> 00:09:41.750
Get dressed. Fall in.

00:09:42.160 --> 00:09:43.120
- Hurry.
- Move, fall in!

00:09:43.120 --> 00:09:43.970
Fall in! Fall in!

00:09:44.070 --> 00:09:44.920
Hurry, hurry!

00:09:45.240 --> 00:09:46.430
- Coming!
- Gather up, now!

00:09:46.430 --> 00:09:47.960
- My shoes!
- Here.

00:09:48.720 --> 00:09:49.560
Move it, move it!

00:09:49.560 --> 00:09:50.400
What is it?

00:09:50.720 --> 00:09:51.870
Can we not get some sleep?

00:09:53.480 --> 00:09:54.870
I can barely open my eyes.

00:09:54.870 --> 00:09:55.750
We've got an emergency.

00:09:56.270 --> 00:09:57.430
Shoes Bai is missing.

00:09:57.720 --> 00:09:58.750
Where did she go?

00:09:58.750 --> 00:09:59.870
We think

00:09:59.870 --> 00:10:01.870
she slipped by the river while bathing.

00:10:02.360 --> 00:10:03.630
Didn't your uncle leave with her?

00:10:03.630 --> 00:10:04.950
Don't talk nonsense, got it?

00:10:05.190 --> 00:10:06.360
Okay, okay, I got it.

00:10:06.360 --> 00:10:07.600
Shout as loud as you can.

00:10:07.600 --> 00:10:09.150
Come on, let's go.

00:10:09.150 --> 00:10:10.030
Move, move!

00:10:10.750 --> 00:10:12.670
Shoes Bai! Shoes Bai!

00:10:13.120 --> 00:10:14.720
Feng Xiaoxiao, watch everyone.

00:10:14.720 --> 00:10:17.120
Shoes Bai! Shoes Bai!

00:10:18.080 --> 00:10:20.750
Shoes Bai! Shoes Bai!

00:10:20.750 --> 00:10:21.600
Shoes Bai!

00:10:21.620 --> 00:10:23.600
Where are you? Come out!

00:10:23.670 --> 00:10:24.510
Shoes Bai!

00:10:24.670 --> 00:10:25.550
Come out!

00:10:25.550 --> 00:10:27.360
Shoes Bai!

00:10:27.360 --> 00:10:34.670
Shoes Bai! Shoes Bai! Shoes Bai!

00:10:34.840 --> 00:10:35.910
- Nothing.
- Check over there.

00:10:35.910 --> 00:10:36.780
- Hurry.
- Okay.

00:10:36.800 --> 00:10:38.960
Shoes Bai! Shoes Bai!

00:10:38.960 --> 00:10:40.480
Nail, found anything?

00:10:40.790 --> 00:10:41.670
Still nothing.

00:10:42.480 --> 00:10:43.320
Then keep looking there.

00:10:43.320 --> 00:10:44.980
I'll take the kids elsewhere.

00:10:44.990 --> 00:10:45.910
Okay, go ahead.

00:10:45.910 --> 00:10:46.780
Be careful.

00:10:46.800 --> 00:10:47.670
- Okay, okay.
- Come on.

00:10:47.670 --> 00:10:48.510
Be careful, Director.

00:10:48.510 --> 00:10:49.370
Everyone, follow me.

00:10:49.390 --> 00:10:50.480
No, not this way.

00:10:50.480 --> 00:10:51.480
Come with me.

00:10:51.670 --> 00:10:52.510
Shoes Bai!

00:10:52.510 --> 00:10:53.870
He Dachui! He Dachui!

00:10:53.870 --> 00:10:54.870
What are you doing here?

00:10:55.360 --> 00:10:56.440
We're looking for Shoes Bai.

00:10:56.440 --> 00:10:57.910
It's pitch-black everywhere.

00:10:57.910 --> 00:10:59.550
Who answers if the kids get hurt?

00:10:59.550 --> 00:11:00.390
Take them back!

00:11:00.550 --> 00:11:01.750
Okay, okay, sure.

00:11:01.790 --> 00:11:03.720
Trainee class, hurry back!

00:11:03.720 --> 00:11:04.670
Back to the dorms. Move.

00:11:06.080 --> 00:11:07.270
Be careful, Director.

00:11:09.350 --> 00:11:10.200
Why stop searching?

00:11:10.200 --> 00:11:11.040
Hurry.

00:11:11.550 --> 00:11:12.910
We haven't found her yet.

00:11:12.910 --> 00:11:14.600
Watch your step. All of you.

00:11:14.600 --> 00:11:15.960
We haven't found her.

00:11:16.270 --> 00:11:17.510
Why stop searching?

00:11:17.510 --> 00:11:18.480
No more searching.

00:11:18.480 --> 00:11:20.150
Why bring the kids out?

00:11:23.360 --> 00:11:24.200
Why not go back?

00:11:25.840 --> 00:11:26.680
Come on.

00:11:28.390 --> 00:11:29.230
Aunt Hua.

00:11:31.750 --> 00:11:32.590
What?

00:11:33.080 --> 00:11:35.120
Shoes Bai left with my uncle.

00:11:42.440 --> 00:11:44.030
My wife is

00:11:44.360 --> 00:11:46.440
a really good person.

00:11:47.790 --> 00:11:48.750
And very capable.

00:11:49.140 --> 00:11:50.030
Yes, exactly.

00:11:50.040 --> 00:11:50.910
A toast.

00:11:56.200 --> 00:11:58.750
Her man died a few years ago.

00:11:59.270 --> 00:12:01.120
Then she began to live alone.

00:12:02.440 --> 00:12:04.390
People love to gossip about widows.

00:12:05.270 --> 00:12:06.870
I fixed bicycles.

00:12:07.720 --> 00:12:09.910
She made tofu.

00:12:09.910 --> 00:12:11.910
We were just one wall apart.

00:12:13.390 --> 00:12:16.600
We looked out for each other.

00:12:17.150 --> 00:12:17.990
And we...

00:12:19.870 --> 00:12:23.750
were noticed by those people.

00:12:24.550 --> 00:12:29.120
They said we had an illicit affair.

00:12:29.910 --> 00:12:31.840
Then we figured,

00:12:32.320 --> 00:12:34.390
we might as well live together.

00:12:36.510 --> 00:12:37.960
- Come on.
- Come on, come on.

00:12:44.270 --> 00:12:50.550
♪Ten years, dead and living♪

00:12:53.910 --> 00:12:59.200
♪Dim and draw apart♪

00:13:00.750 --> 00:13:04.790
♪I don't try to remember♪

00:13:08.120 --> 00:13:09.000
Hurry, go.

00:13:15.840 --> 00:13:16.680
Go on, move.

00:13:26.790 --> 00:13:27.630
Take it with you.

00:13:28.630 --> 00:13:29.480
Thank you, old friend.

00:13:31.030 --> 00:13:31.960
Thank you.

00:13:33.630 --> 00:13:34.470
Please

00:13:35.080 --> 00:13:36.550
look after my wife.

00:13:37.120 --> 00:13:38.750
Rest assured. I will.

00:13:40.390 --> 00:13:41.910
Once you head out,

00:13:42.360 --> 00:13:43.960
turn the corner to the main road.

00:13:44.270 --> 00:13:45.390
Then follow the river upstream.

00:13:46.000 --> 00:13:47.840
Do not leave the main road.

00:14:09.150 --> 00:14:09.990
Go.

00:14:10.960 --> 00:14:11.840
Be careful.

00:14:17.630 --> 00:14:18.750
Alright, let's head back.

00:14:19.270 --> 00:14:20.630
Can I stay here tonight?

00:14:24.630 --> 00:14:26.550
If we don't go back, it may look bad.

00:14:28.270 --> 00:14:29.630
What's bad about it?

00:14:29.630 --> 00:14:31.510
It's so late. Where can she go?

00:14:33.270 --> 00:14:34.110
Come.

00:14:44.630 --> 00:14:47.120
The troupe has just model operas.

00:14:47.120 --> 00:14:49.150
They perform them over and over.

00:14:49.150 --> 00:14:51.150
And the veteran performers in the troupe

00:14:51.150 --> 00:14:53.030
are either dead or gone.

00:14:53.550 --> 00:14:54.670
Only three are left.

00:14:55.790 --> 00:14:58.120
Two guard the gate, one cooks.

00:14:58.960 --> 00:15:00.550
At this rate,

00:15:01.240 --> 00:15:03.870
the old art will be lost.

00:15:04.790 --> 00:15:06.720
What happens to Qinqiang opera down the road?

00:15:07.750 --> 00:15:09.030
Is it finished?

00:15:10.750 --> 00:15:13.910
Qinqiang opera first appeared
in the Western Zhou dynasty.

00:15:16.030 --> 00:15:19.960
Through cold and heat, season
after season, it's lasted

00:15:19.960 --> 00:15:21.720
some three thousand years.

00:15:22.550 --> 00:15:26.390
Dynasties fell over those 3,000 years.

00:15:27.870 --> 00:15:29.870
But Qinqiang opera never died.

00:15:31.000 --> 00:15:31.870
Why not?

00:15:32.360 --> 00:15:36.080
Because its roots are with the people.

00:15:37.030 --> 00:15:38.960
It doesn't belong to any dynasty

00:15:39.390 --> 00:15:41.670
or any one troupe.

00:15:41.670 --> 00:15:43.320
As long as the people live,

00:15:45.030 --> 00:15:47.360
Qinqiang opera will live on.

00:15:47.960 --> 00:15:49.240
Qinling Mountains stand,

00:15:49.910 --> 00:15:51.440
and Qinqiang opera stands.

00:15:57.240 --> 00:15:58.080
Open the door.

00:16:00.750 --> 00:16:01.590
Who is it?

00:16:02.270 --> 00:16:03.120
Who is it?

00:16:03.120 --> 00:16:04.360
Militia. Open the door.

00:16:06.320 --> 00:16:08.240
The hound's nose picked it up again.

00:16:08.240 --> 00:16:09.080
Coming.

00:16:18.270 --> 00:16:19.440
What are you two doing here?

00:16:20.960 --> 00:16:22.390
Drinking.

00:16:23.000 --> 00:16:24.480
Drinking at this hour?

00:16:25.030 --> 00:16:27.030
Drinking till we pass out.

00:16:27.840 --> 00:16:28.680
Who is he?

00:16:30.150 --> 00:16:31.120
A friend of mine.

00:16:32.080 --> 00:16:33.000
A friend from where?

00:16:33.510 --> 00:16:37.240
Hu Sanyuan, lead drummer
with the County Troupe.

00:16:37.790 --> 00:16:38.630
Go.

00:16:39.150 --> 00:16:40.550
Check every room carefully.

00:16:40.550 --> 00:16:41.390
Yes.

00:16:43.080 --> 00:16:44.840
What is this about?

00:16:46.200 --> 00:16:47.960
Move aside. Are you drunk?

00:16:47.960 --> 00:16:49.030
I'm perfectly sober.

00:16:49.390 --> 00:16:51.360
Move aside! Don't make us force you to.

00:16:52.270 --> 00:16:53.110
Go ahead.

00:16:53.510 --> 00:16:54.350
Who are you?

00:17:02.870 --> 00:17:04.960
Take these two to the commune.

00:17:05.150 --> 00:17:06.360
On what grounds?

00:17:06.360 --> 00:17:07.480
What grounds?

00:17:07.480 --> 00:17:08.720
You two were acting suspiciously.

00:17:08.720 --> 00:17:10.000
We clocked you on arrival.

00:17:10.900 --> 00:17:14.260
(Hard work is the boat sailing
on the endless sea of learning)

00:17:14.270 --> 00:17:15.150
Tell the truth.

00:17:15.550 --> 00:17:17.080
Out all night? What were you up to?

00:17:18.670 --> 00:17:20.120
I'm telling you,

00:17:20.120 --> 00:17:21.790
playing mute won't help you.

00:17:21.790 --> 00:17:22.870
There were two pillows on that bed.

00:17:22.870 --> 00:17:23.870
They've already given you two away.

00:17:30.480 --> 00:17:31.550
Fine. Very well.

00:17:31.550 --> 00:17:33.440
So you're digging in to the end.

00:17:35.080 --> 00:17:35.920
You two, out.

00:17:36.630 --> 00:17:37.720
I need to speak with her alone.

00:17:38.480 --> 00:17:39.320
Yes, Director.

00:17:40.960 --> 00:17:41.800
Go.

00:18:22.630 --> 00:18:23.790
On day one

00:18:24.510 --> 00:18:26.630
of our rural performance tour,

00:18:27.240 --> 00:18:28.270
this happened...

00:18:29.720 --> 00:18:31.360
And it had to be you involved.

00:18:32.240 --> 00:18:33.750
I'm honestly surprised

00:18:34.790 --> 00:18:36.000
and deeply disappointed.

00:18:37.550 --> 00:18:39.480
Back at the Song and Dance Troupe,

00:18:39.750 --> 00:18:40.720
you danced Swan Lake.

00:18:42.440 --> 00:18:43.550
I think

00:18:44.510 --> 00:18:45.790
a swan...

00:18:46.070 --> 00:18:48.640
Even if it falls into a mud pit,

00:18:48.920 --> 00:18:50.830
it's still a noble swan, right?

00:18:53.000 --> 00:18:54.030
Am I right?

00:18:58.310 --> 00:19:00.510
I just can't wrap my head around it.

00:19:03.790 --> 00:19:04.630
Tell me.

00:19:05.920 --> 00:19:06.880
What could it be?

00:19:11.720 --> 00:19:13.880
What could make a noble swan

00:19:13.880 --> 00:19:15.310
set aside all that grace

00:19:15.720 --> 00:19:17.270
and willingly stay in the mud,

00:19:17.270 --> 00:19:19.160
mixing with a flock of muddy ducks?

00:19:21.830 --> 00:19:23.510
And I've been wondering...

00:19:25.720 --> 00:19:27.920
A ballet dancer of your standing would

00:19:29.160 --> 00:19:31.030
leave the provincial capital

00:19:31.030 --> 00:19:33.750
for this remote county troupe.

00:19:35.750 --> 00:19:37.750
Was it to be closer to your spouse?

00:19:41.110 --> 00:19:43.200
I heard your spouse's reform through labor

00:19:43.680 --> 00:19:45.640
is in a ravine by this People's Commune.

00:19:49.240 --> 00:19:50.880
How long has it been since you met?

00:19:56.720 --> 00:19:57.880
How sad.

00:19:59.680 --> 00:20:01.790
The farthest distance in this world

00:20:02.240 --> 00:20:05.270
is being this close, yet unable to meet.

00:20:07.240 --> 00:20:08.350
Be honest with me.

00:20:10.070 --> 00:20:11.310
That pillow on the bed.

00:20:11.880 --> 00:20:12.960
Is it his?

00:20:19.830 --> 00:20:20.750
Actually,

00:20:20.750 --> 00:20:23.000
it's easy to prove my hunch.

00:20:23.440 --> 00:20:24.750
I just need to call

00:20:25.510 --> 00:20:27.270
the Revolutionary Committee in his area

00:20:27.640 --> 00:20:29.640
and ask if he is there.

00:20:35.510 --> 00:20:37.480
Told you, playing mute was useless.

00:20:37.480 --> 00:20:39.160
Director, Hu Sanyuan admitted it.

00:20:39.160 --> 00:20:40.240
That pillow on the bed is his.

00:20:40.720 --> 00:20:41.640
He...

00:20:41.640 --> 00:20:43.200
He said the militia came in too soon,

00:20:43.200 --> 00:20:45.270
and it was only an attempted illicit affair.

00:20:45.270 --> 00:20:47.240
An attempt still counts the same.

00:20:47.240 --> 00:20:48.680
In their minds, it already happened.

00:20:48.680 --> 00:20:50.440
- I knew...
- It's you who came in too soon!

00:20:50.440 --> 00:20:51.280
Get out!

00:20:53.070 --> 00:20:53.910
Out!

00:21:03.480 --> 00:21:04.640
Was Hu Sanyuan telling the truth?

00:21:04.640 --> 00:21:05.480
It's true.

00:21:15.680 --> 00:21:17.790
So you've chosen Hu Sanyuan.

00:21:24.030 --> 00:21:25.920
Will your uncle and Shoes Bai be okay?

00:21:29.310 --> 00:21:31.640
I should've told Aunt Hua sooner.

00:21:35.800 --> 00:21:36.640
Hurry.

00:21:36.640 --> 00:21:37.550
Two.

00:21:37.550 --> 00:21:38.390
Faster.

00:21:39.480 --> 00:21:40.320
Hold on.

00:21:42.000 --> 00:21:42.840
Six.

00:21:42.870 --> 00:21:43.740
Go.

00:21:43.750 --> 00:21:44.590
One.

00:21:44.790 --> 00:21:45.790
Ready, five, six, seven, eight.

00:21:45.790 --> 00:21:46.630
Down.

00:21:47.400 --> 00:21:48.750
Two, four.

00:21:49.880 --> 00:21:50.720
Five.

00:21:52.110 --> 00:21:52.950
Down.

00:21:54.640 --> 00:21:55.480
Down.

00:21:56.680 --> 00:21:57.830
- Down.
- Down, down.

00:21:57.830 --> 00:21:58.670
Head down.

00:22:00.160 --> 00:22:01.270
Come on, go down.

00:22:05.160 --> 00:22:06.640
Good. There, that's it.

00:22:07.240 --> 00:22:08.080
Try again.

00:22:09.350 --> 00:22:10.960
Where's your sister?

00:22:11.880 --> 00:22:12.720
Let's see.

00:22:13.030 --> 00:22:13.960
Don't cry.

00:22:14.510 --> 00:22:15.640
Don't cry, okay?

00:22:19.440 --> 00:22:20.880
Is that your sister?

00:22:22.480 --> 00:22:23.350
Laidi!

00:22:24.000 --> 00:22:25.030
Laidi!

00:22:26.000 --> 00:22:26.840
Laidi!

00:22:30.510 --> 00:22:32.680
My girl looks like a whole new person.

00:22:32.680 --> 00:22:35.030
I almost didn't recognize you.

00:22:35.920 --> 00:22:38.160
Half our village came

00:22:38.160 --> 00:22:39.510
to watch the show.

00:22:40.350 --> 00:22:42.070
Your uncle really pulled it off.

00:22:42.640 --> 00:22:44.720
He said you'd pass, and you did.

00:22:45.680 --> 00:22:46.720
My girl now

00:22:47.200 --> 00:22:49.240
is a city girl with commodity grain.

00:22:49.790 --> 00:22:52.400
That's a first for Jiuyangou.

00:22:53.200 --> 00:22:57.070
Our whole family shares my kid's glory.

00:22:57.070 --> 00:22:58.400
What an honor.

00:22:58.400 --> 00:22:59.240
Mom.

00:22:59.510 --> 00:23:00.350
Mom.

00:23:00.790 --> 00:23:01.640
Crying again?

00:23:01.640 --> 00:23:02.880
Come on, come on.

00:23:02.880 --> 00:23:04.240
Let me hold him. Come here.

00:23:04.640 --> 00:23:05.480
Come here.

00:23:06.720 --> 00:23:08.240
Let's go outside.

00:23:08.480 --> 00:23:09.320
Come on.

00:23:09.640 --> 00:23:10.480
Look.

00:23:11.200 --> 00:23:12.110
Look, look.

00:23:12.110 --> 00:23:12.950
Look at this.

00:23:14.550 --> 00:23:16.110
Sis, have some candy.

00:23:18.480 --> 00:23:20.030
What are you all doing?

00:23:20.030 --> 00:23:20.870
Practicing basic skills.

00:23:21.270 --> 00:23:22.440
Can you do opera yet?

00:23:22.750 --> 00:23:23.880
No.

00:23:23.880 --> 00:23:26.310
We bray every morning like a donkey.

00:23:27.680 --> 00:23:28.680
Don't talk nonsense.

00:23:29.160 --> 00:23:30.480
That's vocal warm-ups.

00:23:30.480 --> 00:23:32.270
The more you do it, the clearer it gets.

00:23:32.550 --> 00:23:33.510
How is that donkey braying?

00:23:34.160 --> 00:23:35.000
Don't talk nonsense.

00:23:37.640 --> 00:23:39.640
Your outfit looks nice.

00:23:40.160 --> 00:23:41.640
Uncle bought it for you?

00:23:42.510 --> 00:23:44.790
The troupe issued it.

00:23:45.350 --> 00:23:46.750
They even issued clothes?

00:23:52.750 --> 00:23:54.440
It was supposed to be mine.

00:23:55.680 --> 00:23:56.750
Be careful wearing it.

00:23:57.440 --> 00:23:58.440
Save it for me.

00:24:00.680 --> 00:24:02.440
Emergency assembly!

00:24:04.470 --> 00:24:05.310
What's going on?

00:24:05.310 --> 00:24:06.240
Someone's in trouble.

00:24:07.680 --> 00:24:09.790
Sanyuan, why are you standing there?

00:24:09.920 --> 00:24:10.790
What happened now?

00:24:11.160 --> 00:24:12.110
What happened?

00:24:12.400 --> 00:24:13.640
Come on, Hu Sanyuan.

00:24:13.640 --> 00:24:15.350
Tell everyone what happened.

00:24:16.030 --> 00:24:17.640
Quit that nonsense. Get lost.

00:24:18.070 --> 00:24:19.920
So you do know shame.

00:24:19.920 --> 00:24:20.760
Having an illicit affair.

00:24:21.400 --> 00:24:22.310
He does it wherever he goes.

00:24:22.310 --> 00:24:23.960
- For real?
- Stop making things up.

00:24:24.400 --> 00:24:25.270
Attempted.

00:24:25.270 --> 00:24:27.200
It's there in black and white.

00:24:27.200 --> 00:24:28.880
You stamped it, now you deny it?

00:24:35.750 --> 00:24:37.110
We'll handle this seriously.

00:24:37.110 --> 00:24:38.630
- We'll be going.
- Okay, okay.

00:24:38.880 --> 00:24:39.790
Make way.

00:24:39.790 --> 00:24:40.640
- This way.
- Let's go.

00:24:40.640 --> 00:24:41.480
Take care, sir.

00:24:46.680 --> 00:24:48.640
Who's standing there smirking?

00:24:49.160 --> 00:24:50.640
Is this something to brag about?

00:24:51.920 --> 00:24:53.750
Our top priority now is the show.

00:24:54.350 --> 00:24:56.350
We must make sure it goes smoothly.

00:24:57.920 --> 00:24:58.830
As for those two,

00:24:59.110 --> 00:25:00.640
we'll deal with them back at the troupe.

00:25:01.270 --> 00:25:02.110
Alright.

00:25:02.310 --> 00:25:03.270
Get back to your own work.

00:25:03.680 --> 00:25:04.520
Dismissed.

00:25:11.880 --> 00:25:13.200
What was he thinking?

00:26:00.550 --> 00:26:02.550
Dad! Mom!

00:26:03.070 --> 00:26:04.200
Sis!

00:26:05.790 --> 00:26:07.880
Take me home with you!

00:26:08.750 --> 00:26:10.480
I want to quit!

00:26:13.310 --> 00:26:15.960
Dad, I'm begging you!

00:26:17.680 --> 00:26:20.440
I'll give you my steamed buns. Take me.

00:26:20.640 --> 00:26:22.070
I'm begging you.

00:26:28.240 --> 00:26:29.200
Mom!

00:26:30.350 --> 00:26:31.750
Please!

00:26:32.680 --> 00:26:34.750
I can't take it anymore.

00:26:35.240 --> 00:26:37.550
Take me home!

00:26:38.680 --> 00:26:40.480
Mom...

00:27:05.680 --> 00:27:06.520
Nail.

00:27:07.830 --> 00:27:08.720
What can I do?

00:27:11.480 --> 00:27:12.510
What's that look?

00:27:13.030 --> 00:27:15.480
"Attempted illicit affair". So refined.

00:27:16.000 --> 00:27:16.840
Keep at it.

00:27:17.790 --> 00:27:18.880
- Move it over.
- You brat.

00:27:18.880 --> 00:27:20.240
What do you even know?

00:27:22.110 --> 00:27:22.950
Mi Lan.

00:27:23.270 --> 00:27:24.880
Great show last night. Congrats.

00:27:24.880 --> 00:27:25.720
Thanks.

00:27:45.270 --> 00:27:46.640
Nothing happened, okay?

00:27:47.000 --> 00:27:48.510
- I'll explain later.
- Get lost.

00:27:48.510 --> 00:27:50.110
I had no choice.

00:27:51.300 --> 00:27:52.160
"Get lost"?

00:27:52.160 --> 00:27:53.030
That's all you ever say.

00:27:53.790 --> 00:27:54.630
Hu Sanyuan.

00:27:55.550 --> 00:27:56.390
Come here.

00:27:58.000 --> 00:28:00.070
Tonight, play the Japanese squad leader.

00:28:00.680 --> 00:28:01.520
Why?

00:28:01.720 --> 00:28:03.350
Master Song is busy with the night snack.

00:28:03.350 --> 00:28:04.190
You cover for him.

00:28:04.720 --> 00:28:06.880
I haven't slept since yesterday.

00:28:06.880 --> 00:28:07.750
Not my problem.

00:28:07.750 --> 00:28:09.640
We're short. It's you. Settled.

00:28:10.660 --> 00:28:11.510
Playing a squad...

00:28:11.510 --> 00:28:12.400
Do I have lines?

00:28:12.400 --> 00:28:13.240
Yes.

00:28:14.640 --> 00:28:15.640
I'd better hurry.

00:29:25.940 --> 00:29:29.860
(Ningzhou County Qinqiang Opera Troupe)

00:29:46.640 --> 00:29:47.960
How is the Japanese soldier your uncle?

00:29:50.270 --> 00:29:51.790
Is there anything he won't do?

00:29:51.790 --> 00:29:54.000
Drums, an illicit affair, a soldier...

00:29:56.680 --> 00:29:59.110
It seems a public interrogation

00:29:59.110 --> 00:30:01.200
won't get us the secret code.

00:30:01.200 --> 00:30:02.310
The listening device?

00:30:02.310 --> 00:30:03.640
Been installed.

00:30:03.640 --> 00:30:05.960
When the mother and son meet,

00:30:05.960 --> 00:30:08.110
listen to what they say.

00:30:08.110 --> 00:30:10.830
We may pick up some clues.

00:30:10.830 --> 00:30:12.720
Bring the old woman up.

00:30:12.720 --> 00:30:13.880
Bring her up.

00:30:13.880 --> 00:30:14.880
Old woman.

00:30:14.880 --> 00:30:16.750
Captain Hatoyama wants you up.

00:30:16.750 --> 00:30:17.590
Get lost.

00:30:26.830 --> 00:30:29.680
Ma'am, do you know where this is?

00:30:29.680 --> 00:30:31.200
Kempeitai.

00:30:31.750 --> 00:30:33.000
Your son

00:30:33.000 --> 00:30:35.920
is about to meet his end here.

00:30:35.920 --> 00:30:39.200
When someone commits a crime,

00:30:39.200 --> 00:30:41.960
and his mother can save him,

00:30:41.960 --> 00:30:43.720
but chooses not to,

00:30:43.720 --> 00:30:48.640
isn't that cruel of her?

00:30:49.200 --> 00:30:51.070
You harm our people,

00:30:51.070 --> 00:30:53.110
and expect us to take the blame?

00:30:53.110 --> 00:30:56.160
Even an old woman like me?

00:30:58.070 --> 00:30:58.920
Great.

00:30:58.920 --> 00:31:01.200
Then go see your son.

00:31:01.200 --> 00:31:03.920
Great! Bravo!

00:31:03.920 --> 00:31:06.030
Bravo!

00:31:06.030 --> 00:31:06.880
Well acted!

00:31:07.680 --> 00:31:08.640
Bravo!

00:31:13.160 --> 00:31:15.510
Take Li Yuhe over there.

00:31:15.510 --> 00:31:16.350
Yes.

00:31:16.680 --> 00:31:22.240
♪Bring Li Yuhe♪

00:31:37.830 --> 00:31:39.440
Director, the police are here.

00:31:43.400 --> 00:31:44.240
Hello, sir.

00:31:44.680 --> 00:31:45.670
- Hello, comrades.
- Hello, sir.

00:31:45.680 --> 00:31:46.540
Thank you for coming.

00:31:46.560 --> 00:31:47.420
This way, please.

00:31:47.600 --> 00:31:48.440
Come.

00:31:48.470 --> 00:31:50.900
♪Pass your bravery to me♪

00:31:50.920 --> 00:31:54.030
♪So that I dare face the fierce beasts♪

00:31:55.640 --> 00:31:57.720
I got so furious onstage.

00:31:58.240 --> 00:31:59.640
I nearly lost it.

00:31:59.640 --> 00:32:02.000
I almost took Hatoyama out.

00:32:02.550 --> 00:32:03.480
You fool.

00:32:05.130 --> 00:32:10.420
♪The red lantern♪

00:32:10.430 --> 00:32:14.240
♪Oh, Father♪

00:32:15.590 --> 00:32:19.840
♪Your spiritual wealth can fill every cart♪

00:32:19.860 --> 00:32:21.340
♪And every boat♪

00:32:21.350 --> 00:32:23.270
♪A thousand carts still aren't enough♪

00:32:23.310 --> 00:32:25.790
Watch the actress, okay?

00:32:25.790 --> 00:32:27.510
You're totally off beat.

00:32:28.400 --> 00:32:30.070
Here. You do it. Come on.

00:32:30.070 --> 00:32:31.680
I'm the director, okay?

00:32:31.680 --> 00:32:33.160
Hurry up. Watch the actress.

00:32:37.790 --> 00:32:39.400
Know why I play the squad leader?

00:32:40.030 --> 00:32:40.870
I get lines.

00:32:41.240 --> 00:32:42.310
You can only play a soldier.

00:32:42.310 --> 00:32:43.550
Just stand there holding a gun?

00:32:45.000 --> 00:32:46.880
I've got tons of stage experience.

00:33:00.270 --> 00:33:03.790
Captain Hatoyama gives you five minutes.

00:33:03.790 --> 00:33:05.270
Hand over the secret code,

00:33:05.270 --> 00:33:06.790
or you'll all be executed.

00:33:12.440 --> 00:33:13.280
Young lady.

00:33:14.110 --> 00:33:15.830
Five minutes left.

00:33:15.830 --> 00:33:17.110
Hand over the secret code.

00:33:17.310 --> 00:33:20.270
Then your whole family can live.

00:33:20.270 --> 00:33:21.110
Got it?

00:33:22.920 --> 00:33:23.760
Say it.

00:33:25.960 --> 00:33:27.920
The secret code.

00:33:30.920 --> 00:33:31.760
Focus.

00:33:33.000 --> 00:33:34.740
Fire!

00:33:34.750 --> 00:33:41.400
♪Arise, wretched of the earth♪

00:33:41.430 --> 00:33:47.640
♪Arise, convicts of hunger♪

00:33:47.640 --> 00:33:53.840
♪Reason thunders in its crater♪

00:33:53.840 --> 00:34:00.800
♪This is the eruption of the end♪

00:34:01.000 --> 00:34:02.920
Down with Japanese imperialism!

00:34:02.920 --> 00:34:05.270
Long live the Communist Party!

00:34:05.270 --> 00:34:07.920
Long live Chairman Mao!

00:34:07.920 --> 00:34:09.070
Down with the Japanese soldiers!

00:34:09.070 --> 00:34:10.720
Down with the Japanese soldiers!

00:34:10.720 --> 00:34:12.680
Down with the Japanese soldiers!

00:34:12.680 --> 00:34:15.550
Down with Japanese imperialism!

00:34:16.240 --> 00:34:18.680
Down with the Japanese soldiers!

00:34:22.070 --> 00:34:23.310
Down with imperialism!

00:34:24.830 --> 00:34:25.960
Down with the Japanese soldiers!

00:34:32.640 --> 00:34:34.680
Stop! Those are my shoes!

00:34:36.270 --> 00:34:37.960
Down with the Japanese soldiers!

00:34:38.240 --> 00:34:41.350
Close the curtain! Close it! Now!

00:34:41.880 --> 00:34:43.160
(Ningzhou County Qinqiang Opera Troupe)
Down with the Japanese soldiers!

00:34:43.400 --> 00:34:44.920
Down with the Japanese soldiers!

00:34:47.830 --> 00:34:48.720
Who is it?

00:34:48.720 --> 00:34:50.110
Militia. Open the door.

00:34:53.270 --> 00:34:54.960
Get your woman. Come with us.

00:34:56.270 --> 00:34:58.030
Japanese soldiers sure are hateful.

00:34:58.030 --> 00:35:00.440
We must return the kids' shoes fast.

00:35:00.440 --> 00:35:01.280
Or they can't practice basic skills.

00:35:01.300 --> 00:35:02.550
Hu Sanyuan! Hu Sanyuan!

00:35:02.550 --> 00:35:03.440
- What?
- Come with me.

00:35:03.440 --> 00:35:04.680
- Give me the gun.
- What for?

00:35:04.680 --> 00:35:05.720
Don't ask. Let's go.

00:35:21.350 --> 00:35:22.510
What are you staring at? Move.

00:35:39.160 --> 00:35:40.000
Come in.

00:35:44.230 --> 00:35:45.760
Comrade Hu Sanyuan is usually...

00:35:45.760 --> 00:35:47.470
Director, Hu Sanyuan is here.

00:35:49.150 --> 00:35:50.190
This is Hu Sanyuan.

00:35:52.360 --> 00:35:53.710
Go squat by that wall first.

00:35:55.800 --> 00:35:56.640
Hurry, hurry.

00:36:03.710 --> 00:36:05.630
Actually, he's usually

00:36:06.320 --> 00:36:07.920
not much of a problem.

00:36:15.960 --> 00:36:19.320
He wanted a shortcut, a side path.

00:36:20.480 --> 00:36:23.000
Then he fell down the mountain.

00:36:25.150 --> 00:36:29.480
I shouldn't have given him that flashlight.

00:36:39.190 --> 00:36:40.030
Hu Sanyuan.

00:36:41.110 --> 00:36:43.670
After review by the Revolutionary Committee,

00:36:44.550 --> 00:36:45.960
you'll receive a major demerit.

00:36:46.630 --> 00:36:48.280
No drumming for the next year.

00:36:48.800 --> 00:36:49.880
Report to the canteen as a helper.

00:36:50.440 --> 00:36:51.480
Do you understand?

00:36:52.700 --> 00:36:56.140
(Main Office)

00:37:48.510 --> 00:37:50.190
If you're hurting inside,

00:37:51.550 --> 00:37:52.710
just let yourself cry.

00:37:58.280 --> 00:37:59.670
Go back and rest.

00:38:00.840 --> 00:38:02.110
No need to stay with me.

00:38:54.320 --> 00:38:55.440
Why didn't you tell me?

00:38:58.110 --> 00:39:00.630
How? You told me to get lost.

00:39:04.380 --> 00:39:08.500
(Together)

00:39:08.510 --> 00:39:10.670
Still stargazing? No sleep?

00:39:11.670 --> 00:39:13.320
I keep feeling something's happening.

00:39:16.400 --> 00:39:17.240
What is it?

00:39:17.880 --> 00:39:20.030
I don't know. I just feel uneasy.

00:39:20.480 --> 00:39:21.320
Why?

00:39:22.000 --> 00:39:23.030
Maybe your uncle rattled you.

00:39:27.110 --> 00:39:28.510
I feel a little dizzy.

00:39:28.510 --> 00:39:31.070
Don't sway. You're making me panic.

00:39:31.070 --> 00:39:31.910
I'm not swaying.

00:39:32.400 --> 00:39:33.710
Feels like the ground is shaking.

00:39:35.640 --> 00:39:36.550
Stop it.

00:39:36.550 --> 00:39:37.630
Not my fault.

00:39:38.630 --> 00:39:40.000
My head's spinning.

00:39:41.110 --> 00:39:42.190
What's going on?

00:39:44.510 --> 00:39:45.480
What is this?

00:39:45.480 --> 00:39:46.630
(Ningzhou County Qinqiang Opera Troupe)

00:39:46.630 --> 00:39:47.470
An earthquake.

00:39:48.630 --> 00:39:49.470
An earthquake!

00:39:50.150 --> 00:39:50.990
An earthquake!

00:39:51.350 --> 00:39:52.190
An earthquake!

00:39:52.190 --> 00:39:53.110
An earthquake!

00:39:56.670 --> 00:39:59.670
Early morning of July 28, 1976.

00:39:59.670 --> 00:40:01.670
The earth shook violently.

00:40:02.710 --> 00:40:06.190
The Tangshan earthquake stunned the world.

00:40:06.960 --> 00:40:07.960
After the earthquake,

00:40:07.960 --> 00:40:10.320
the troupe rushed back to town,

00:40:10.320 --> 00:40:14.440
- and built earthquake shelters.
- Have you been to Tangshan?

00:40:14.440 --> 00:40:16.320
Everyone lived there,

00:40:16.510 --> 00:40:19.920
starting a new life.

00:40:20.590 --> 00:40:21.840
It seems like a prefecture-level city.

00:40:22.630 --> 00:40:23.880
Flat as far as you can see.

00:40:24.480 --> 00:40:25.670
Where is Tangshan anyway?

00:40:26.440 --> 00:40:27.880
Not far from Beijing, I guess.

00:40:28.320 --> 00:40:30.440
Why call it "shan" (mountain) if it's flat?

00:40:31.710 --> 00:40:33.000
You've got me stumped.

00:40:34.800 --> 00:40:35.920
- Master Song.
- What?

00:40:35.920 --> 00:40:37.710
Director Huang wants you at a meeting.

00:40:37.710 --> 00:40:38.570
A meeting?

00:40:38.630 --> 00:40:39.470
Hurry up.

00:40:41.320 --> 00:40:43.070
Sanyuan, help knead the dough.

00:40:43.070 --> 00:40:44.070
We need to rest the dough.

00:40:49.630 --> 00:40:50.480
Come on, hurry.

00:40:51.670 --> 00:40:52.510
Nail this side down tight.

00:40:57.300 --> 00:40:59.820
(Caixiang, as if we were back
at our first summer.)

00:41:06.070 --> 00:41:06.910
Director.

00:41:14.320 --> 00:41:15.230
Comrades.

00:41:16.000 --> 00:41:18.030
I worked it out with the scale.

00:41:19.150 --> 00:41:20.630
Tangshan,

00:41:21.710 --> 00:41:24.510
as the crow flies from Chairman Mao
and the CPC Central Committee,

00:41:25.150 --> 00:41:27.110
is only about 150 kilometers.

00:41:27.880 --> 00:41:30.630
Tangshan is about 1,000 kilometers from us.

00:41:31.030 --> 00:41:32.320
Even from that far away,

00:41:32.960 --> 00:41:35.280
we felt the earth shake.

00:41:36.070 --> 00:41:38.510
That shows how severe the quake was.

00:41:39.440 --> 00:41:42.030
The CPC Central Committee
has sent forces to Tangshan.

00:41:42.480 --> 00:41:44.230
That shows how serious this is.

00:41:46.360 --> 00:41:47.880
We all served in the military.

00:41:48.960 --> 00:41:49.880
We may be discharged,

00:41:50.440 --> 00:41:51.550
but we do not back down.

00:41:52.760 --> 00:41:54.630
Our test has come.

00:41:55.800 --> 00:41:58.000
We must charge to the front,

00:41:58.800 --> 00:42:00.000
win this battle,

00:42:00.630 --> 00:42:01.550
and protect the troupe.

00:42:02.050 --> 00:42:02.960
Are you determined?

00:42:02.960 --> 00:42:03.800
Yes.

00:42:05.110 --> 00:42:07.000
An earthquake is an unseen foe.

00:42:07.540 --> 00:42:08.800
(How am I worse than him?)
We're exposed.

00:42:08.800 --> 00:42:11.000
(Just tell me if you need any help.)
The situation is very complicated.

00:42:11.630 --> 00:42:13.960
(After all, we were a couple.)
We must be ready

00:42:14.510 --> 00:42:15.440
for anything.

00:42:18.800 --> 00:42:19.670
Stop it. That's my pillow.

00:42:19.670 --> 00:42:20.510
Liu Ke! You!

00:42:20.510 --> 00:42:21.590
Stop it. Careful.

00:42:21.590 --> 00:42:22.440
Put the pillow down.

00:42:27.430 --> 00:42:28.280
Move aside!

00:42:28.280 --> 00:42:29.120
Stop fighting!

00:42:33.150 --> 00:42:34.710
Little brat, what are you doing?

00:42:34.710 --> 00:42:36.030
What are you doing? Get it back.

00:42:36.030 --> 00:42:37.070
Get out of the rain. Hurry.

00:42:41.550 --> 00:42:42.960
You little troublemaker.

00:42:44.480 --> 00:42:46.030
Stop running. Stop fighting.

00:42:46.030 --> 00:42:47.800
He drummed two days ago.

00:42:48.400 --> 00:42:49.360
Yesterday, he played a Japanese soldier.

00:42:49.360 --> 00:42:50.320
Today, he's kneading dough.

00:42:50.760 --> 00:42:52.070
So what does your uncle actually do?

00:42:52.320 --> 00:42:53.230
Quit messing around.

00:42:53.230 --> 00:42:54.070
I'm asking you.

00:42:54.220 --> 00:42:55.110
Laidi!

00:42:55.110 --> 00:42:56.840
Zhang Heiwa! What are you doing?

00:42:56.840 --> 00:42:58.070
Hurry, come catch the water!

00:42:58.510 --> 00:42:59.550
- Hurry up.
- My clothes are wet.

00:42:59.550 --> 00:43:00.400
Careful. Hurry.

00:43:00.410 --> 00:43:01.480
Can I not go?

00:43:01.670 --> 00:43:02.800
Stop messing around.

00:43:03.110 --> 00:43:03.980
Use your hands.

00:43:05.020 --> 00:43:06.940
=The Lead=
(Preview)

00:43:09.160 --> 00:43:11.410
This is the first money you've ever earned.

00:43:11.410 --> 00:43:12.280
Keep it safe.

00:43:13.110 --> 00:43:14.970
- Make way.
- This Tangshan earthquake...

00:43:14.970 --> 00:43:15.890
Make way.

00:43:15.890 --> 00:43:18.120
has caused extremely serious casualties.

00:43:18.120 --> 00:43:19.880
We can't just write letters.

00:43:20.210 --> 00:43:21.520
We should also donate money,

00:43:21.780 --> 00:43:22.840
just like the teachers.

00:43:25.790 --> 00:43:26.660
Comrade Hua Caixiang,

00:43:27.150 --> 00:43:28.290
your application for divorce is,

00:43:28.290 --> 00:43:29.520
for the time being, denied.

00:43:29.520 --> 00:43:30.440
I've got it.

00:43:30.440 --> 00:43:31.430
Got what?

00:43:31.750 --> 00:43:32.680
I'm pregnant.

00:43:37.000 --> 00:43:41.620
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:43:43.090 --> 00:43:47.930
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:43:49.370 --> 00:43:53.560
♪We met and brushed past♪

00:43:55.120 --> 00:44:02.420
♪Your shadow drifted out of sight♪

00:44:16.790 --> 00:44:20.540
♪The stove fire blazed in my dream♪

00:44:22.140 --> 00:44:27.710
♪Lit up the tracks of pearly tears♪

00:44:28.830 --> 00:44:32.890
♪In my dream, water sleeves flew♪

00:44:34.020 --> 00:44:39.610
♪Hiding a lifetime of love♪

00:44:40.770 --> 00:44:44.970
♪The Qinling Mountains
crossed the stage♪

00:44:46.010 --> 00:44:51.640
♪Spring water brewed strong wine♪

00:44:52.810 --> 00:44:57.500
♪Sheep moved through the valley♪

00:44:58.180 --> 00:45:03.350
♪It felt like a promise
from another life♪

00:45:04.020 --> 00:45:09.050
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:45:10.080 --> 00:45:15.510
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:45:15.890 --> 00:45:21.170
♪If I chose again, I'd still roam♪

00:45:22.120 --> 00:45:27.930
♪All over this sunlit plateau♪

00:45:27.930 --> 00:45:33.350
♪The dream ends; the curtain falls♪

00:45:33.900 --> 00:45:39.410
♪Moonlight washes off this stage makeup♪

00:45:39.960 --> 00:45:44.920
♪The one in the mirror wears gray hair♪

00:45:45.940 --> 00:45:51.220
♪Already sang all my joy and sorrow♪

00:45:52.020 --> 00:46:01.050
♪Already shouted across Qinchuan Plain♪